TT-Line Gaming Regulations 2014

I, the Lieutenant-Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, make the following regulations under the TT-Line Gaming Act 1993 .

17 November 2014

A. M. BLOW

Lieutenant-Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

PETER GUTWEIN

Treasurer

1. Short title
    These regulations may be cited as the TT-Line Gaming Regulations 2014 .

2. Commencement
    These regulations take effect on 8 December 2014.

3. Prescribed fee for issue of gaming licence
    For the purposes of section 4(4) of the TT-Line Gaming Act 1993 , the prescribed fee is 100 fee units.

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 26 November 2014

These regulations are administered in the Department of Treasury and Finance.
